gnutls_sign_get_hash_algorithm(3)                                                                 gnutls                                                                 gnutls_sign_get_hash_algorithm(3)

NAME
       gnutls_sign_get_hash_algorithm - API function

SYNOPSIS
       #include <gnutls/gnutls.h>

       gnutls_digest_algorithm_t gnutls_sign_get_hash_algorithm(gnutls_sign_algorithm_t sign);

ARGUMENTS
       gnutls_sign_algorithm_t sign
                   is a signature algorithm

DESCRIPTION
       This function returns the digest algorithm corresponding to the given signature algorithms.

SINCE
       3.1.1

RETURNS
       return a gnutls_digest_algorithm_t value, or GNUTLS_DIG_UNKNOWN on error.

REPORTING BUGS
       Report bugs to <bugs@gnutls.org>.
       Home page: https://www.gnutls.org

